data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER: Great spacious home in the very desirable Stone Creek neighborhood.Large living room,impressive fireplace+ an open concept to the dining, kitchen, breakfast area.This well planned home is perfect for the family to enjoy + entertain friends and family.The gourmet kitchen boasts of an oversized island, lots of cabinetry, hard surface island and countertops, gas cooktop,the SS refrigerator can stay. Lots of windows in this home which provides plenty of natural light.Office is located on the first level at the front part of the home.The  Master suite, is on the first level, with space  for extra seating area ..plus an upscale large adjoining bathroom.  There are 2 more bedrooms  on the first level with their own bathrooms. Second level provides Media room, gameroom, 4th bedroom plus a full bath. The park, community swimming pool, jogging trails and schools are located nearby.(See Private Remarks below*).
